action.action-desc: Mr. McConnell submitted the following resolution; which was considered and agreed to

form.official-title: Electing Laura C. Dove, of Virginia, as Secretary for the Minority of the Senate.

section.text: That Laura C. Dove of Virginia be, and she is hereby, elected Secretary for the Minority of the Senate, effective Friday, August 2, 2013.
